{
  "stem": "27340.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was active in-- in guiding these people down various side roads and tracks in the woods and so on until in fact we met up again with a colleague of mine who then took over and took them further southwards.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you operated on your own?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ja, but within this framework.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, each one was entirely on his own.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was somebody fully in charge who I met in Paris when I first arrived there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was given basic instructions, but his name, obviously, was not known to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My name, perhaps, was known to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The names of my colleagues on either side-- the one up front and the one at, at, at, at the end of my run-- I knew only by face.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Certainly, I didn't know their names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't know my name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the whole idea was that if we were to be caught and if we were to be tried or held responsible for this sort of thing, we would not be in a position to give away any-- any other information.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think-- it is a very good question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we went by train, and we were met somewhere near the-- near, near, near, near a station.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- I-- I think it was a lorry or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were dispersed and dropped off in that sort of fashion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a-- it was a clandestine operation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was totally against the interests of HM government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I think in order to be fair, there was a lot of collusion and connivance by the Belgians and the French who saw this.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
